Te7 4 chiunn Khi3-khu7
Chu2-jit8-oh8 sou2 tioh8 eng7 e5 khi3-khu7 u7 chin che7, chong2-si7 Jit8-pun2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 iau2 si7 ti7 iu3-ti7 e5 si5-tai7, sou2-i2 m7-bian2 tioh8 eng7 chin che7 chinn5 lai5 hak hiah e5 khi3-khu7, chong2-si7 e7-bin7 sou2 sia2 chiah e5 khi3-khu7, chi3-chio2 tioh8 ai3 eng7, m7-si7 chin kui3 e5 mih8, sou2-i2 tak8 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e7-thang siat-ti3.
(1) Ji5-tong5 e5 i2-a2: Li7-iong7 hoe7-tng5 chiong toa7 lang5 e5 i2-a2 hou7 gin2-na2 che7, si7 chin m7 ho2. Na7 beh an2-ni eng7 tioh8 eng7 kha-tah8-tai5, m7-thang hou7 gin2-na2 e5 kha tong7-tong7-hainn3. Hek8-chia2 ui7-tioh8 ji5-tong5 Tek8-piat8 cho3 se3-chiah i2-a2 si7 choe3 ho2.
