Te7 5 chiunn Keng-hui3.
Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 keng-hui3, eng-kai kau3-hoe7 tioh8 ai3 hu7-tam. Beh siat-lip8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 tong-jian5 tioh8 ai3 hui3-iong7. Bo5 chinn5 si7 be7-thang cho3 sim2-mih8. In-ui7 kin-a2-jit8 chin che7 lang5 teh siunn7, gou7-kai2 kong2 thoan5-to7 si7 chi2 u7 thoan5 hou7 toa7-lang5, ia7 chhin-chhiunn7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 siunn7 kong2 si7 kau3-hoe7 e5 hu3-siok8 mih8 e5 khoan2, sou2-i2 koan-khoann2 hou7 thoan5-to7-chia2 u7 goan7-i3, chong2-si7 tui3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 siat-pi7 sou2 ai3 eng7 e5 chinn5 m7-ai3 chhut, chit e5 thang khoann3 ti7 kau3-hoe7 long2 bo5 he7 ji5-tong5 ti7 gan2-tiong nih8, siat-su2 tai7-ke na7 khak-sin3 chai ji5-tong5 si7 bin5-a2-jit8 e5 kau3-hoe7-oan5, ia7 na7 ji5-tong5 bo5 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 lai5 kau3-iok8 be7-thang hou7 kau3-hoe7 kian7-choan5, hoe7-iu2 un2-tang3 chin hoann-hi2 ui7-tioh8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 beh hian3 chin che7 chinn5.
U7 kau3-hoe7 chhiann2 bok8-su i2-goa7 koh chhiann2 1-2 e5 thoan5-to7-su, chong2-si7 m7-bat thiann kong2 u7 chhiann2 chit8 e5 choan-kang ui7-tioh8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 lai5 hian3-sin e5 thoan5-to7-su, chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni tui3 ji5-tong5 e5 kau3-iok8 leng2-tam7, tui3 kau3-hoe7 si7 chin m7 ho2. Teng2-jit8 tui3 Bi2-i2-bi2-hoe7 e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 tiunn2-lo2 thiann-tioh8 chit8 e5 sit8-oe7, ¡§Ti7 Sam-chiu Toyohasi, 15 ni5-cheng5 u7 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7 chin toa7-keng, chong2-si7 kin-a2-jit8 khi3 ka7 khoann3, sou2 chhun e5 lang5 long2 si7 lau7-peh-a3 kap lau7-m2-a3, siat-su2 chiah e5 lang5 na7 si2-liau2, kiam2-chhai2 lian5 kau3-hoe7 kap sin3-tou5 long2 bo5 liau2-liau2. Siat-su2 ti7 hia 15-16 ni5-cheng5 na7 tui3 chong-kau3-tek e5 ji5-tong5 kau3-iok8 u7 jiat8-sim, chiah e5 lau7-a-peh a-m2 in si2-liau2, ia7 tek-khak u7 chheng-lian5 lau5-teh chiah tioh8.¡¨
Sit8-chai7 kau3-hoe7 na7 bo5 chhut kau3-giah8 e5 keng-hui3, hou7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 hoat-tian2, hit e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 chian5-tou5 thang kong2 put-chi2 thang han5-sim. Chhin-chhiunn7 kau3-hoe7 eng7 sia7-le2-kim hou7 bok8-su, iah8 tioh8 eng7 sia7-le2-kim hou7 ui7-tioh8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 cho3 kang e5 lang5. Ti7 Bi2-kok kin7-lai5 u7 khai-si2 siat Chu2-jit8-oh8 bok8-su, che si7 chin ho2 e5 hian7-siong7. Kau3-hoe7 mui2-ni5 beh phian-che3 inn7-soan3 e5 si5, m7-thang be7-ki3-tit chiong Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 keng-hui3 he7 ti7 hit tiong-kan.
Te7 6 chiunn Hak8-seng.
Chhin-chhiunn7 Jit8-pun2, Ki-tok-kau3 boe7 phou2-pian3 e5 kok-ka, beh bou7-chip8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng si7 put-chi2 khun3-lan5 e5 su7. U7 sou2-chai7 m7-na7 si7 in e5 pe7-bo2, lian5 sio2 hak8-hau7 e5 sian-sinn to hoan2-tui3 hak8-seng khi3 hu3 Chu2-jit8-oh8. Koh ti7 hak8-hau7 e5 hak8-seng ia7 u7 khoann3-khin khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng e5 khoan2. Chit-khoan2 chong7-thai7, sou2-i2 beh bou7-chip8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng m7 si7 iong5-inn7 e5 su7. Jim7-li2 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 siat-pi7 u7 chin ho2, na7 bo5 hak8-seng lai5 si7 be7 chiann5 hak8-hau7. Sou2-i2 tioh8 an2-choann2 chiah e7 gau5 bou7-chip8 hak8-seng, si7 lan2 chiah e5 teh keng-eng5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 su7-giap8 e5 lang5 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 bun7-te5. Chit le2-pai3 u7 20 lang5 lai5, ia7 au7 le2-pai3 u7 50 lang5 lai5, an2-ni hak8-seng sou2 u7 pian3-tong7, un2-tang3 oh-tit cho7-chhut ho2 e5 hak8-hau7. Hoan2-tng2, na7 koh chit8-geh8-jit8 chin kin2 teh cheng-ka, hek8-si7 50 lang5 a2-si7 100 lang5, ia7 m7 si7 chin ho2 e5 khoan2-sit. Kian7-choan5 e5 hak8-hau7 si7 hak8-seng sou2 chiam7-chiam7 cheng-ka, ia7 tui3 chit khoan2 e5 hak8-hau7 chiah e7-thang si-siat ho2 e5 siat-pi7. Tann chiong chiah e5 su7 pun cho3 kui2 hang7 lai5 kong2 hit e5 tai7-khai3.
(1) Hak8-seng e5 chu-keh<BR>Ke3-siok8 3 pai2 i2-siong7 lai5 Chu2-jit8-oh8, koh iok beh ke3-siok8 lai5 e5 ji5-tong5 chiah thang hou7 i cho3 hak8-seng. Jit8-pun2 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8, chiong na7 sou2 u7 lai5 e5 ji5-tong5, bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5 long2 ka7 khoann3-cho3 hak8-seng che si7 toa7 chho3-gou7. Beh cho3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng, ia7-si7 tioh8 u7 cho3 hak8-seng e5 chu-keh. Chu2-jit8-oh8 m7 si7 kan-ta ji5-tong5 thit-tho5 e5 sou2-chai7. In-ui7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 si7 si-heng5 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 e5 sou2-chai7, sou2-i2 beh cho3 hit e5 hak8-seng e5 si5, chin7-liong7 tioh8 hou7 in e5 pe7-bo2 the5-chhut jip8-hak8-goan7 chiah ho2. Na7 an2-ni pe7-bo2 e7 chu7-jian5 liau2-kai2 chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 bok8-tek.
(2) Ho2 e5 hak8-hau7 e5 lat8. (Bou7-chip8 hak8-seng e5 hoat-tou7) <BR>Ho2 e5 hak8-hau7 u7 khip-in2 hak8-seng e5 lat8. Hak8-seng lai5 khoann3 chit8-pai2, na7 siunn7 kong2 chit-keng hak8-hau7 u7 sim-sek, u7 lou7-eng7, hit e5 gin2-na2 chu7-jian5 e7 ke3-siok8 koh lai5. Ji5-tong5 chin seng5-sit8, na7 bo5 sim-sek bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 hak8-hau7 tek-khak bo5 beh koh lai5. U7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 eng7 thng5-a2, a2-si7 pat8-mih8 lai5 tioh8 hak8-seng, che sit8-chai7 chin m7 tioh8 e5 hoat-tou7. Na7 eng7 piann2 a2-si7 pat8-mih8 lai5 chu7-chip8 e5 ji5-tong5, bo5 hiah e5 piann2 a2-si7 pat8-mih8 e5 si5 chiu7 bo5 lai5. Mui2 le2-pai3-jit8 na7 eng7 piann2 a2-si7 pat8-mih8 hou7 in, kiam2-chhai2 beh chio-chip8 100 lang5, a2-si7 200 lang5 si7 iong5-inn7 e5 su7. Chong2-si7 chit-khoan2 hoat-tou7 tek-khak be7-thang tit-tioh8 ke3-siok8 lai5 e5 hak8-seng, chin che7 lang5 eng7 hak8-seng sou3 lai5 khoann3 hak8-hau7 e5 seng5-soe (heng-ong7 a2-si7 soe-bi5), chong2-si7 che si7 m7 tioh8. Hak8-seng sou3 bo5-lun7 20 e5 a2-si7 30 e5 bo5 iau3-kin2, na7 u7 oan5-choan5 si-heng5 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 chiu7 ho2, phou2-thong e5 hak8-hau7 si7 eng7 koan5-ui teh koan2 hak8-seng e5 chhut-sek8, chong2-si7 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 tioh8 eng7 thiann3 lai5 koan2 in e5 chhut-sek8. Sou2-i2 na7 m7 si7 u7 sim-sek koh iu2-ek e5 hak8-hau7, chiu7 bo5 lat8 thang khip-in2 hak8-seng.
(3) Ko3-jin5 e5 cho3-kang (Bou7-chip8 hak8-seng e5 hoat-tou7 2) <BR>Hak8-seng bo5 chu7 khi2-thau5 chiu7 ka-ki7 lai5, tek-khak tioh8 tui3 chit-peng5 u7 lang5 ka7 in2-chhoa7. Chhin-chhiunn7 kou2-cha2 An-tek-liat8 chhoa7 Pi2-tek lai5 chiu7-kin7 Ia5-sou e5 khoan2, na7 bo5 ko3-jin5-tek e5 in2-chhoa7 ji5-tong5 be7 lai5 Chu2-jit8-oh8. Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 kau3-oan5 tioh8 ka-ki7 in2-chhoa7 hak8-seng lai5, tek-khak m7-thang pai3-thok pat8-lang5. Na7 thak8 Bu2-ti3 sian-sinn e5 toan7-ki3, u7 sia2 kong2 i pun2-sin ka7 lang5 chioh be2-chhia khi3 seh8, bou7-chip8 ji5-tong5 lai5 khui Chu2-jit8-oh8. Chu2-jit8-oh8 e7 seng7-tai7, si7 in-ui7 sian-sinn ka-ki7 cho3 ko3-jin5-tek e5 kang, koh chheng-lian5 Kiong7-le7-hoe7 tek-khak tioh8 siat chhin-chhiunn7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 ui2-oan5, ui7-tioh8 bou7-chip8 hak8-seng lai5 cho3 kang. Sit8-chai7 ko3-jin5-tek e5 cho3 kang chiah si7 hou7 hak8-seng ke-thinn e5 pi3-koat. (Au7-ki5 thai7-siok8)
